OL,3,CYoung men with epilepsy run half
OL,4,Cmarathon for charity
OL,6,FCiaran Monaghan, 27, and Will
OL,7,FChadwick, 24, started an inclusive
OL,8,Frunning club in Leeds after bonding
OL,9,Fover their shared experience of
OL,10,Fepilepsy.
OL,12,FOn Saturday 21 February they both took
OL,13,Fpart in the Leeds Winter Warmer half
OL,14,Fmarathon, at Temple Newsam, in aid of
OL,15,FLeeds based charity Epilepsy Action
OL,16,Fhoping to raise #500.
OL,18,FThey surpassed their target raising
OL,19,Fmore than #700, now they are hoping to
OL,20,Fraise #1500.
