OL,6,FCiaran experienced his first seizure
OL,7,Fin February 2025. He said, "I didn't
OL,8,Fhave another until September last
OL,9,Fyear, and it completely threw me. This
OL,10,Fis what led me to getting an epilepsy
OL,11,Fdiagnosis and it was a big shock.
OL,13,F"Since my diagnosis, I started a
OL,14,Fsocial media page to chat to people
OL,15,Fabout their mental health and run 5km
OL,16,Fwith them.
OL,18,F"It's been great meeting so many
OL,19,Fpeople from the local community,
OL,20,Fincluding Will and others living with
OL,21,Fepilepsy."
