OL,6,FWill was diagnosed with epilepsy at
OL,7,Fthe age of 13.
OL,9,FHe said he struggled to accept it
OL,10,Fadding, "I was an ignorant and
OL,11,Fstubborn teenager and didn't want to
OL,12,Fchange anything about my life when I
OL,13,Fwas diagnosed.
OL,15,F"It's only over time that I've
OL,16,Frealised I'm going to have to give
OL,17,Fsome things up and alter my life a bit
OL,18,Fso I can live a normal, healthy
OL,19,Flifestyle."
