OL,6,FTogether they founded the 'Monaghans
OL,7,FMiles' running club, after Will
OL,8,Fappeared in one of Ciaran's social
OL,9,Fmedia videos.
OL,11,FCiaran said he set the club up as a
OL,12,Fway to battle the mental health
OL,13,Fconsequences of the medication he had
OL,14,Fto take for the condition. He told ITV
OL,15,FCalendar, "When I first started my
OL,16,Ftablets for it, I went through severe
OL,17,Fdepression as part of the side effects.
