OL,6,F"With Will having had epilepsy for
OL,7,Fover 11 years, he's been like a
OL,8,Fsupport cushion and we have made
OL,9,Freally good friends from each other."
OL,11,FPhilippa Cartwright, Director of
OL,12,FFundraising at Epilepsy Action, said:
OL,13,F"Will and Ciaran have done an amazing
OL,14,Fjob creating an inclusive, welcoming
OL,15,Fspace where everyone - including
OL,16,Fpeople with epilepsy - can feel
OL,17,Fcomfortable exercising together.
